        <ezobject:attribute xmlns:ezremote="http://ez.no/ezobject" ezremote:id="8760" ezremote:identifier="intro" name="Summary" type="ezxmltext">
          <section xmlns:image="http://ez.no/namespaces/ezpublish3/image/" xmlns:xhtml="http://ez.no/namespaces/ezpublish3/xhtml/" xmlns:custom="http://ez.no/namespaces/ezpublish3/custom/">
            <paragraph>Today we completed migration of the database configuration to use the soon to be open sourced voting solution plugin required for the digg sigma / digg clone projects.</paragraph>
            <paragraph>With sevenx_digg extension we will include the design templates and datatype needed to vote for content objects within our lamp php cms eZ Publish 6.</paragraph>
            <paragraph>With the digg clone project we will be releasing our full current site sources and the full mysql database required to start people off with a reference platform to use to build their own digg clone based websites. The digg clone project home page is also coming soon to <link href="https://clone.digg.one">https://clone.digg.one</link></paragraph>
          </section>
        </ezobject:attribute>
